msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Keeper Mendicant"
msgstr "帳の神の僧侶"

msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Keeper Mendicant"
msgstr "帳の神の僧侶"

msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"When your order crumbled, and the world fell into darkness soon thereafter, "
"you were driven to wander in your struggle to survive.  But your oath is "
"immortal, and when the stars are right you will find a way to serve the "
"Shrouded King once more."
msgstr ""
"宗派が崩壊し、その後すぐに世界が暗闇に陥ったとき、生き延びるめの戦いの中で"
"放浪の旅に追い込まれました。しかし、あなたの誓いは不滅であり、星が正しく"
"輝くとき、再び「帳の神」に仕える道を見つけるでしょう。"

